data.message: You can interview me after Shift!

message:
SENIORS: Hey y'all! As some of you know, I'm currently involved in a TV reporting class and will be doing my final story of the year on Cru/Shift. I'm hoping to talk to a couple of you about your experience in Cru and what it's like being in a "religious affiliated" group on campus for a majority of your college experience. SOOO, if you're willing to be interviewed on camera this Wednesday before or after Shift, please let me know in the comments or in a personal message.

Also, there are about 20 students in my class who will watch this and, based on conversations, none of them are believers. This is a super cool opportunity to talk about Cru, the love of Christ, and why He is worthy of our praise and worship during college. Like I said, let me know in the comments or message me if you're interested.

Thanks guys!

P.S. This means I'll be filming parts of Shift on Wednesday. So, don't freak out if there's a camera in front of you!
